[workspace]
members = ["blockchain/client", "blockchain/connector", "blockchain/connector/utilities", "blockchain/contracts/aipsc", "blockchain/contracts/asc", "blockchain/contracts/tendermint-ipsc", "blockchain/contracts/ethereum-ipsc", "blockchain/contracts/csc", "blockchain/cosmos-proto", "blockchain/events", "blockchain/gateway", "blockchain/simulator", "blockchain/contracts/common", "conf-trace", "core/backup", "core/grpc", "core/service", "core/threshold", "core/utils", "core-client", "blockchain/inclusion_proofs/ethereum", "blockchain/inclusion_proofs/ethereum-triedb", "blockchain/contracts/bsc", "test-utils", "kms-connector"]
exclude = ["backward-compatibility"]
resolver = "2"

[workspace.dependencies]
actix-cors = "=0.7.0"
aes = "=0.8.4"
aes-prng = "=0.2.1"
alloy-dyn-abi = "=0.8.20"

async-trait = "=0.1.83"

bincode = "=1.3.3"

cosmwasm-schema = "=2.1.4"
cosmwasm-std = "=2.1.4"
cw-controllers = "=2.0.0"
cw-storage-plus = "=2.0.0"
cw-utils = "=2.0.0"
cw2 = "=2.0.0"
futures = "=0.3.31"
hex = "=0.4.3"
http = "1.2.0"
itertools = "=0.13.0"
k256 = "=0.13.4"
lazy_static = "=1.5.0"
mockall = "=0.13.0"
opentelemetry = "=0.27.1"
paste = "=1.0"
prost = "=0.13.4"
prost-build = "=0.13.4"
prost-types = "=0.13.4"
rand = "=0.8.5"

schemars = "=0.8.21"

serde_json = "=1.0.132"
serial_test = "=3.2.0"
sha2 = "=0.10.8"
sha3 = "=0.10.8"
strum = "=0.26.3"
strum_macros = "=0.26.4"
sylvia = "=1.1.0"
sylvia-derive = "=1.1.0"
tendermint-proto = "=0.40.0"
tfhe = "=0.11.2"
tfhe-csprng = "=0.5.0"
tfhe-versionable = "=0.4.0"
tfhe-zk-pok = "=0.4.0"
thiserror = "=2.0.11"
tonic = "=0.12.3"
tonic-build = "=0.12.3"
tonic-health = "=0.12.3"
tower = "=0.5.2"
tower-http = "=0.6.2"
tracing-actix-web = "=0.7.15"
tracing-appender = "=0.2.3"
tracing-opentelemetry = "=0.28.0"
typed-builder = "=0.20.0"

[workspace.dependencies.actix-web]
version = "=4.9.0"
features = ["macros"]

[workspace.dependencies.aipsc]
path = "./blockchain/contracts/aipsc"

[workspace.dependencies.backward-compatibility]
path = "./backward-compatibility"

[workspace.dependencies.bsc]
path = "./blockchain/contracts/bsc"

[workspace.dependencies.clap]
version = "=4.5.20"
features = ["derive"]

[workspace.dependencies.conf-trace]
path = "./conf-trace"

[workspace.dependencies.contracts-common]
path = "./blockchain/contracts/common"

[workspace.dependencies.cosmos-proto]
path = "./blockchain/cosmos-proto"

[workspace.dependencies.csc]
path = "./blockchain/contracts/csc"

[workspace.dependencies.distributed-decryption]
path = "./core/threshold/"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.events]
path = "./blockchain/events"

[workspace.dependencies.kms]
path = "./core/service"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.kms-blockchain-client]
path = "./blockchain/client"

[workspace.dependencies.kms-blockchain-connector]
path = "./blockchain/connector"

[workspace.dependencies.kms-common]
path = "./common"

[workspace.dependencies.kms-core-utils]
path = "./core/utils"

[workspace.dependencies.kms-grpc]
path = "./core/grpc"
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.reqwest]
version = "=0.12.12"
features = ["json", "rustls-tls"]
default-features = false

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "=1.0.217"
features = ["derive", "rc"]

[workspace.dependencies.tendermint]
version = "0.40.0"
features = ["secp256k1"]

[workspace.dependencies.tendermint-rpc]
version = "=0.40.0"
features = ["websocket-client"]

[workspace.dependencies.tokio]
version = "=1.43.0"
features = ["full"]

[workspace.dependencies.tracing]
version = "=0.1.41"
features = ["log"]

[workspace.dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "=0.3.19"
features = ["fmt", "std"]

[workspace.package]
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = ["Zama"]
license = "BSD-3-Clause-Clear"
publish = true

[profile.release]
lto = "fat"

[profile.release.package]

[profile.dev]
opt-level = 1

[profile.dev.package."*"]
opt-level = 3

[profile.test]
opt-level = 3

[profile.test.package]

[profile.bench]
debug = true

[profile.bench.package]

[profile.release-lto-off]
inherits = "release"
lto = "off"

[profile.release-lto-off.package]

[profile.wasm]
opt-level = "z"
inherits = "release"
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"

[profile.wasm.package]

[[example]]
path = "examples/decrypt.rs"
name = "decrypt"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["bin"]

[[example]]
path = "examples/decrypt_response.rs"
name = "decrypt-response"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
crate-type = ["bin"]
